This profile opted out of bundled-skill seeding (`hermes skills opt-out`).
Delete this file to re-enable sync on the next `hermes update`.

# Tracked in dotfiles and symlinked into ~/.hermes/ by install.sh so the opt-out
# reproduces on a fresh machine. Without it, the first `hermes` run would seed
# ~73 bundled skills into the symlinked ~/.hermes/skills (= this repo), polluting
# it. Bundled skills are instead read in place via config.yaml skills.external_dirs.
